<main class="container">
  <h1>Submit a Request for Proposal</h1>
  <p class="lead">For enterprise AI strategy engagements beyond our standard consulting sessions, we scope custom implementations with not-to-exceed pricing and full P4D3-structured deliverables.</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>What to Include in Your RFP</h2>
    <p>To scope your engagement accurately, please provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Organization overview</strong> — Industry, size, and current technology stack</li>
      <li><strong>Objective</strong> — The specific AI outcome you are trying to achieve</li>
      <li><strong>Current state</strong> — Existing AI initiatives, data infrastructure, and governance posture</li>
      <li><strong>Constraints</strong> — Timeline, budget range, compliance requirements, data sovereignty requirements</li>
      <li><strong>Decision criteria</strong> — How you will evaluate proposals</li>
      <li><strong>Stakeholders</strong> — Key contacts and decision-makers involved</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>What You Receive</h2>
    <p>Every scoped engagement includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Current State Analysis — audit of your existing infrastructure and AI readiness</li>
      <li>Future State Goal — clearly defined architectural vision</li>
      <li>Gap Analysis — precise evaluation of what bridges are required</li>
      <li>Strategic Roadmap — phased deployment blueprint</li>
      <li>Not-to-exceed pricing — complete financial predictability</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">Custom engagements typically range between $5,000 and $100,000 depending on scope, dependencies, and complexity.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Submit Your RFP</h2>
    <p>Send your RFP directly to:</p>
    <p><strong><a href="mailto:james.szmak@elevationary.com">james.szmak@elevationary.com</a></strong></p>
    <p class="muted">We respond to all RFPs within 2 business days. For time-sensitive inquiries, book a <a href="/consulting-15/">15-minute introductory call</a> first.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Or Start with a Consultation</h2>
    <p>Not ready for a full RFP? A consultation is the fastest path to a scoped proposal.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/consulting-15/">15-Minute Introductory Session — $99</a></li>
      <li><a href="/consulting-60/">60-Minute AI Strategy Session — $399</a></li>
      <li><a href="/consulting-90/">90-Minute Enterprise Deep-Dive — $598</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
